{"product_id": "48190", "page": 1, "page_order": 2, "recommended": false, "date": "2018-02-18", "text": "What I hate the most are games specifically made to \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 with you. Every \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 mission is preceded by equally \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 unskippable cinematic. I swear to god I spent at least 1 hour of the 45 I've played watching cinematics. Even the damn map takes 2 seconds to visualize because, of course, you have to watch a \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 animation.\nI beg of you people, do not make my mistake and give Ubisoft money. Better spend them on crack, booze and hookers.", "hours": 46.6, "username": "globetrotter", "products": 204, "early_access": false}
