{"product_id": "48190", "page": 2, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2018-01-27", "text": "Assassin's Creed Brotherhood continues the convoluted story of the Assassin's Creed series where Assassin's Creed Two left off. The game takes most of what worked in Assassin's Creed Two and refined and streamlined them. If you liked the first two games you will likely enjoy this one as well.\nHighlight of the game was chasing an old parkcouring Catholic man through a cathedral. 7/10", "hours": 27.3, "user_id": "76561197965841229", "username": "Paths", "products": 137, "early_access": false}
