{"product_id": "48190", "page": 14, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-22", "text": "Download the latest version of Uplay. Link:\nIt's the better version of Uplay, which Ubisoft regularly updates, tweeks, and fixes, before you buy AC:Brotherhood. Because Steam give you a version of Ye Olde! Uplay, which will eventually give you a bad time.\nGoogle Authenicator (for iphones and androids)/Windows Authenicator (for Windows Phones/Nokia) - To prevent more infamous pirates from stealing your account in the first place.\nLast Pass - So you won't lose the password to your Ubisoft account (and more important things) ever again.\nMake a separate e-mail account just for gaming, mainly G-Mail and/or any strong and unhackable e-mail severs. Because Yahoo! is hacker bait.\nIf someone steals your account and enables 2-Step Verification, go log into your\naccount and send in your support ticket. There's a working customer support, unlike in Uplay's first dark days, so contact them.\nIf that doesn't work, there's other methods to get help.\n\n\nand\n(Full game review coming soon.) :D\nMultiplayer -\nI'm too busy going through the tutorials, plus, will eventually getting killed. 'Cause everyone's better at it than me.", "hours": 0.2, "user_id": "76561198031855571", "username": "pachirisuGrrl33", "products": 22, "found_funny": 2, "early_access": false}
