{"product_id": "48190", "page": 28, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-07-06", "text": "I'd say this is a good game to continue Ezio's life and the future of the Brotherhood. So far I've never got to play this game even though I played Revelations and the 2nd game and so on..... Finally got to play Brotherhood. The graphics are pretty decent for a game that came out 6-7 years ago . Fighting style is the same as any other Assassin's Creed game. I'd give Brotherhood a good 7/10 for Story , 9/10 for Gameplay and 6/10 for Physics. Worth the money and time . Can't wait for Assassin's Creed Origins . Even though the previous games didn't have good ratings/reviews. I'm still loyal to the Assassin's Creed franchise.", "hours": 15.3, "username": "The Bad Guy", "products": 152, "early_access": false}
