{"product_id": "48190", "page": 37, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-03-27", "text": "So far the game runs smoothly on the pc, but the camera movements aren't as satisfying smooth as one would expect, even though it's running at a constant 60fps. This isn't a bother if you put your sensitivity to a higher setting than the default. Other than that this game is amazing. Still one of the best games i've played since young, and i was willing to rebuy it, i never finished it, but i wanted to now, and it's still as good as i remember.\nI would recommend a controller as this game was just better with one, and it's the only game i'll say that for because of the camera. But this game deserves to be played and it definitely beats the latest ones. Except black flag that one was awesome but still it's one of those games you wish devs were still making...\nI'll give it a 8 to 9/10...", "hours": 3.3, "user_id": "76561198153405096", "username": "OCDjunky", "products": 50, "early_access": false}
