{"product_id": "48190", "page": 41, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-02-12", "text": "This game follows the story after Assassin's creed 2.\nright after ezio exits the vault, he met uncle mario and the story of brotherhood began. In this game, ubisoft offered more side missions than AC2, the main story is shorter but more epic than AC2. There are more equiments in brotherhood than any before it, for example crossbow, poisonous darts and even parachutes.\nPro:\nGraphic is ok\nstory\ncharacter\nside missions\ngameplay\nCon:\nbugs\nuplay\nOverall: 9/10\nIt is still my second favorite AC game", "hours": 30.8, "username": "SH0KR", "products": 67, "early_access": false}
