{"product_id": "48190", "page": 46, "page_order": 8, "recommended": false, "date": "2017-01-04", "text": "Why do you put this available on mac when it's not working?? Shame...\nEdit: For those who gonna say this fix or that fix: Tryed every single one, run on blind mode even, got to the actual game keyboard doesn't work. Is that a game that works? not for me. Still gonna play it on bootcamp when i have the chance but sell a game for a platform that the user as to hack the game and for my case doesn't even work shouln'd be selled.\nBe aware that I'm writing this review based on a mac game not a windows one.", "hours": 0.5, "username": "kirloi", "products": 53, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
