{"product_id": "48190", "page": 61, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-09-09", "text": "It falls short of Assassin's Creed 2, but It was better than Assassin's Creed Revelations and Assassin's Creed 3.\nIn terms of gameplay it takes the same formula of Assassin's Creed 2 and refresh it.\nIn terms of plotline, well, think of it as a really big stand-alone expansion to ACII.\nIn terms of graphics, they ain't the best, but when the game was released the graphics were top of the line.", "hours": 54.8, "username": "The most Glorious one", "products": 239, "early_access": false}
