{"product_id": "48190", "page": 63, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-08-12", "text": "Overall this game is a little bit worse than AC2: This is better than AC2 in many ways, BUT This is worse than AC2 in some ways also. The game is awesome, definitely a must-have for people who've played AC2. But if you haven't, this game will make very little sense to you since it's a continuation of the story.", "hours": 6.9, "username": "\u2720 The Italian Spaniard \u269c", "products": 37, "early_access": false}
