{"product_id": "48190", "page": 65, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-07-19", "text": "Man, a Assassin's creed game from back when they were still good, and not just mediocre. There isn't much at all to say, if your a fan of these games, you'll be a fan of this one. I personally still think the second one is better, but this one isn't too far off. The game is fun, beautiful, has an engaging plot, and even sound nice. I can't say anything about this one is bad, but I can say it isn't quite as good as the two that cam before it.", "hours": 45.2, "username": "Reeze The Vampire", "products": 301, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
