{"product_id": "48190", "page": 67, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-06-26", "text": "Did you like Assassins Creed 2?\nYes?\nWell then ive got great news for you: You will like this game too. The controls and invironment look and feel the same so you dont really have to adapt. I finished AC2 half a year ago as of writing this and as soon as i got in my first fight i quickly remembered the controls.\nLong story short, play AC and AC2 before you play Brotherhood otherwise youll miss out on 2 awesome games!\n100% Recommended! Would buy again!", "hours": 22.0, "username": "Ic3w4Tch-San", "products": 164, "early_access": false}
