{"product_id": "48190", "page": 93, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-11-29", "text": "It is not a bad game, nor a great one neither.\n- Good graphics for the release year.\n- A charismatic protagonist.\n- It is fun, sometimes.\n- I like the economy mechanic, but it is so unreal.\n- It is a beautiful game.\n- The soundtrack isn't remarkably good, but not remarkably bad either.\n- The open world isn't a great deal.\n- Voice acting.\n- Not very good story.\n- Boring gameplay.\n- Ubisoft.\n- Uplay.\n- You don't play as Altair.\nBasicaly it is the same of all the years, nothing really shines in Brotherhood, but still is fun, so, yes, i recommend it.", "hours": 14.5, "username": "Braquiador", "products": 455, "early_access": false}
