{"product_id": "48190", "page": 93, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-11-29", "text": "A great sequel to one of the best Assassin's Creed protagonists.\n+ Great Story\n+ Great Background Music\n+ Great Supporting Characters\n+ Great Missions/Side Missions\n+ Great Combat\n+ Good Open World\n+ Good Graphics\n+ Tombs\n+ Recruit Assassins\n- Contrast Issues\n- Only 1 City where as Assassin's Creed II had 5 Cities\n9.5/10 - Amazing\nFirst time completed: 11/07/13\nSecond time completed: 09/12/15", "hours": 48.9, "username": "Ahmed", "products": 8, "early_access": false}
