{"product_id": "48190", "page": 93, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-11-28", "text": "The Banjo-Tooie of the series.  Improves much more than the last game.  Brotherhood introduces the Creed system in which you can recruit people to join your Creed.  More story and another twist.\nGameplay 10/10\nSound 7/10\nStory 9/10\nOverall an improvement from Assassin's Creed 2 and that game was a amazing.  Slight problems for the controller but can be fixed easily with a google search.", "hours": 16.0, "username": "MPkNight", "products": 623, "early_access": false}
