{"product_id": "48190", "page": 98, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-10-28", "text": "Play AC II and fall in love with Ezio, then play Brotherhood and keep falling in the deep abyss.\nOne of the best written AC's.\nWar Machine missions will make you cry for that 100%\n10/10 will continue to cry till i go through Bomber mission for the 50th time\n(it does run on Windows 10)", "hours": 49.6, "username": "Oliveira", "products": 195, "early_access": false}
