{"product_id": "48190", "page": 114, "page_order": 5, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-07-02", "text": "I LOVE this game!\nWhy still not recommending. Because of UBISOFT and UPLAY.\nI'm playing single player, but in the main menu the Multiplayer and UPLAY options are grayed out, and within the game can't reach the Investments. UBISOFT is \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ing giving everybody \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665t, and says all is ok, but it's not - you can find others complaining about it, too. So \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 YOU Ubisoft...\nThat's why I put thumb down... This game is \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ing\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665me off!", "hours": 43.0, "user_id": "76561198078570758", "username": "borbelytomi", "products": 115, "found_funny": 3, "early_access": false}
