{"product_id": "48190", "page": 120, "page_order": 7, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-05-28", "text": "Terrible i want my money back, I have a Dell XPS 18' All in One. Its not terribly slow, but isn't terribly fast. I downloaded This game excited to play it, But EVERYTIME the UPLAY launcher opens up, it says that the program has stopped working than Crashes, Ive redownloaded this game more than 4 times and even tried it without updating it, and it worked when it wasnt updated. But didn't want to allow me to play the game without signing in. I just want my money back at this point.", "hours": 40.4, "username": "Darthflyer", "products": 58, "early_access": false}
