{"product_id": "48190", "page": 122, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-05-15", "text": "This game was my introduction to Assassin's Creed, and I absolutely loved it.\nApart from the Apple of Eden, which is the single worst ultimate weapon in existence.", "hours": 46.2, "user_id": "76561198087095738", "username": "IAmTheZump", "products": 84, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "48190", "page": 122, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-05-15", "text": "The Best Assassin's creed I've ever played.\nAfter Revelation, Assassin's creed Series became bored. But Brotherhood gave great experience. Battle is quite good. Only One Full Sync is better as revelation did. I purchased it with Revelations and Black flag, AC2. Also. In the side-mission, It has full sync challenges! I love it!", "hours": 57.2, "username": "ImperatorCaesar", "products": 49, "early_access": false}
