{"product_id": "48190", "page": 125, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-04-12", "text": "Its a good game and keeps with the flow of the second. However this game offers some premium level \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ery on the ending, with all this extra \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665t and a solid 10 minutes of unskippable credits feels like the game dragged on when it could have easily ended 4 hours ago.", "hours": 17.1, "username": "Deathtouch (\u9ede\u7a74)", "products": 182, "early_access": false}
