{"product_id": "48190", "page": 126, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-04-06", "text": "This game is tremendously fun. The single player campaign provided me with over 80 hours of entertainment (I'm somewhat of a completionist), and even after that, I just had fun free-running across the enormous open-world map. The storyline is extremely interesting and I don't have a reason to dislike this game. The combat is also extremely satisfying, with chaining kills together being easy to learn, but difficult to master.\nOverall, this is one of my favorite games from one of my favorite franchises.", "hours": 117.9, "username": "kedron", "products": 447, "early_access": false}
