{"product_id": "48190", "page": 127, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-03-22", "text": "Amazing game. A lot like AC2 but even better in every way except the length. I found that the end came a bit quickly after playing the second game and expecting something similar. I suppose I could have explored more and done more of the side missions, but it felt like I was maybe half way through exploration and side quests and then I was finding myself at the end of the story. Well I shouldn't focus this review on that as the game itself was incredible and the story was great. Overall it was better than the second one and I can't wait to start Revelations to complete this trilogy.\nSide note, If you didn't play AC2 first, do that for sure, then play this.", "hours": 28.1, "username": "Icza", "products": 251, "early_access": false}
