{"product_id": "48190", "page": 128, "page_order": 7, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-03-13", "text": "Do not buy this game. They don't mention that you have to have a uPlay account and uPlay as third party software, which I'm pretty sure they're required to mention. Still haven't gotten to play it because of stupid fracking uPlay, as even after I got an account, my uPlay just stopped working. Ubisoft are a terrible, persistent company with relatively good games, but no game is worth letting them try to make uPlay a thing.\nPros:\n-Is otherwise a great game that I played years ago on Xbox.\nCons:\n-UPLAY UPLAY UPLAY UPLAY\nDo not buy until they stop doing this kind of crap.", "hours": 0.5, "username": "Smugly", "products": 95, "early_access": false}
