{"product_id": "48190", "page": 129, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-03-09", "text": "Assasin's Creed Brotherhood is a very exciting game, where you live and breath as Ezio Auditore, the legendary assasin. I like how Assasin's Creed Brotherhood has used colourful and good graphics. I also like how Assasin's Creed has used many fashionable assasination moves, i.e if you press f, you lock in a target and air assasinate it.  Overall, the game is well made, and I especially like the graphical effects. This game is totally awesome! I recommend you to play this game!", "hours": 3.6, "username": "\u2b50\ufe0fAssasin\u2b50", "products": 6, "early_access": false}
