{"product_id": "48190", "page": 130, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-02-27", "text": "This is a good game and you really need to get it, one of my favourite Assassin's Creed and also if you have a low graphic card like Intel Core i3-2310M CPU 2.10GHz (Not really low but it is not highest also after i3 is i5 and i7 (Best in Intel i7) So if you have a graphic card like mine or a little better then buy this version Assassin's Creed Brotherhood! It can also run I and II but I find Brotherhood is the best version out of I and II.", "hours": 22.3, "user_id": "76561198172514065", "username": "Dark Justice", "products": 65, "early_access": false}
