{"product_id": "48190", "page": 136, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-01-24", "text": "10/10\nPLUS: Great continuation of AC2. Story continues and is still very creative and inspiring. Rome is absolutely beautiful (if you've seen it live, you'll be surprised!). Game runs perfectly on my PC and looks better than AC4:Black Flag which runs very slow. Brotherhood is very long and the amount of side activities is huge! Creating your own Assasin Guild is fantastic and is implemented well. Soundtrack is a piece of art!\nMINUS: Can't think of any! Buy it!", "hours": 52.5, "user_id": "76561198096659530", "username": "tomek.nowobilski", "products": 35, "early_access": false}
