{"product_id": "48190", "page": 156, "page_order": 6, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-11-14", "text": "Fun to play but extremely bad bugs exists, tip is to turn graphics to 'console specs' i.e. do not have above 60Hz on the graphics and so on. Otherwise you'll have huge troubles with one of the 'L' missions (to avoid spoilers).\nThey've skimped on quality assesement and it's noticeable through the whole game.... suspect some frustrating times parkouring.\nBig two minuses are the bugs and the story, and the story part is probably just not my cup of tea.\nOtherwise a really good game!", "hours": 25.0, "user_id": "76561198028397391", "username": "DaBaxter", "products": 499, "early_access": false}
