{"product_id": "48190", "page": 172, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-08-01", "text": "Imagine if you will, Assassin's Creed II but with ever more polished gamplay, a new and good (in animus) storyline with a great antagonist who you'll really want to kill. But, then right at the end as you leave the animus, imagine if you will that the Ubisoft Montreal team took ALL THE COCAINE then finished the game. Done. That's Assassin's Creed: Brotherhood\n10/15 - \"Ubisoft Montreal took ALL THE COCAINE\"", "hours": 10.9, "username": "happycarrot50", "products": 414, "early_access": false}
