{"product_id": "48190", "page": 174, "page_order": 8, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-07-18", "text": "This game is amazing dont get me wrong. But the fact that ubisoft is still forcing us to use the peice of crap uplay is \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665t. This game itself is awesome, but the hoops you have to jump throught to actuly open the game is not right. I give the game a 8/10. 3/10 if you count in uplay.\npros+\n+good storyline\n+fun gameplay\n+feeling like a badass\ncons-\n-UPLAY\n-somewhat outdated graphics\n-the long process of starting the game", "hours": 52.3, "username": "Cesar the suspicious pizza guy", "products": 80, "early_access": false}
