{"product_id": "48190", "page": 175, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-07-13", "text": "This is my first on Assassin's Creed series. After I had played this game, I started to search for the entire series and then easily got addicted. This game is epic, completely epic, Third-Person view action game. Ezio will help you drive into the content and the great plot of this game. There is real place and real myth feature in this game. You should play this! Very recommend.", "hours": 3.5, "username": "Unmaker", "products": 163, "early_access": false}
