{"product_id": "48190", "page": 178, "page_order": 2, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-07-01", "text": "When I saw that this was available for a mac, I bought it without reading the reviews. A big mistake. On a mac, I had trouble getting the game to load and once it did, I played once and it never worked again. It would either fail to load (quit unexpectedly) or when it did, the keyboard wouldn't work. Seemed like a great game though, big pity it doesn't run well/easily on macs.", "hours": 20.6, "username": "takeo211", "products": 6, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "48190", "page": 178, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-07-01", "text": "One of the best games I have ever played, probably the best Assassin's Creed game because its the perfect mix for a good story and a good multiplayer.", "hours": 25.2, "user_id": "76561198047918356", "username": "k99888401", "products": 30, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "48190", "page": 178, "page_order": 4, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-06-30", "text": "THIS IS BAD!!!! IM USING MAC BOOK AIR 2014, BUT TOTALLY CANT OPEN. WHEN I PRESS PLAY IN STEAM LIBRARY,IT KEEP POP OUT A WINDOW THAT SAID \"QUIT UNEXPECTEDLY' !!! I TRY ANOTHER WAY TO OPEN THE GAME, FINALLY I DONE IT,BUT ANOTHER PROBLEM POP OUT!!! MY KEYBOARD DOESNT WORK AT ALL, I CAN USE MY MOUSE TO LOOK AROUND AND TAKE OUT THE ASSASSIN DAGGER IN HIS HAND BY PRESSING LEFT CLICK ON MOUSE, BUT KEYBOARD TOTALLY NO PERFORMANCE!!!\nPLEASE STEAM!! PLEASE!!! GIVE A SOLUTION FOR ME!!! I WASTE $5 FOR NOTHING???????????????", "hours": 0.5, "username": "Eddie's Starve", "products": 73, "early_access": false}
