{"product_id": "48190", "page": 183, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-06-19", "text": "Solid maybe recommendation.\nPlay it if you're a fan of the franchise, if you'd like to see the gameplay expanded and refined with new elements and improvements, or if you'd like to see how the Assassin's Creed mechanics work out in multiplayer. If you don't have a lot of time to devote, or you just want to see the new plot developments, you might as well just watch the ending on YouTube. The gameplay is a lot of fun and a definite improvement over the other games, but the plot is a rehash of two levels from 2 and there's not much new plot.\nFull review here:", "hours": 24.8, "user_id": "76561197987047936", "username": "The Squid", "products": 345, "early_access": false}
