{"product_id": "48190", "page": 188, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-04-26", "text": "It's pretty good, the gameplay is fun as hell. Even if you're used to it on a console (like I was) and are just coming back to it because you enjoyed it the first time, the controls are really quite easy to pick up with the parkour element being a simple combination of the left mouse button and the space bar. I mean come on.\nAlso, the multiplayer, a few words, if you wanna actually find a game, don't try and play at like 5 in the morning or something, because, it probably won't work, if you wind up in a 1/6 lobby, leave and try again, if the lobby you end up in has more than 2 players waiting, stay there. The multiplayer is very much NOT dead and still has one of the nicest multiplayer gameplay experiences I have ever played.", "hours": 9.9, "username": "NeonDicks", "products": 118, "early_access": false}
