{"product_id": "48190", "page": 188, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-04-22", "text": "AC Brotherhood is a lot like II (which is good) and features the same protagonist. Instead of going all over northern Italy, you now stay (mostly) in Rome. Rome is a very big and interesting place, so it certainly doesn't feel limited; but it is a bit less varied.\nGameplaywise there are some nice improvements. The biggest and most interesting one is that you can now recruit other assassins, who can either help you out in combat, or perform missions for money. Besides this there are some small improvements, such as the ability to ride horses inside the city, and some noticable improvements in the controls. The story, however, is not as engaging as that of AC II.\nOverall, a very solid and enjoyable game, even if I enjoyed II a little more. 8/10 compared to AC II's 9/10.", "hours": 44.9, "username": "Fred2000", "products": 601, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "48190", "page": 188, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-04-20", "text": "This game is great!\nBut i cant play it due to forgeting my uplay account and my last email used for it is gone.\nI hate makeing accounts just to play a game.", "hours": 41.0, "username": "Highuse", "products": 186, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "48190", "page": 188, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-04-19", "text": "Its amazing game! same as previous series, you play as Ezio Auditore da Firenze. Fight the Borgia and bring back the Rome from destruction and bring back the Apple of Eden!\nRome city look awesome. Atmosphere of roma so real, from the building, how people speak, etc. Its 100% Italy. The combat is easy to learn and easy to use. You can recruit people to join the Brotherhood, and you can call them when you're fight. 100% synchronization is the challenge in here. Ignite the Borgia tower to unlocked the building around the tower. Crossbow and Gun blade is too overpower weapon. Power of Apple of Eden is very strong! Its easy to get money from bank!", "hours": 58.2, "username": "feat. Riadi", "products": 167, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "48190", "page": 188, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-04-18", "text": "This was my favorite assassins creed game, it was REALY fun, when i was playing this, it felt like i was realy there. best game for 19.99", "hours": 21.1, "username": "pkg", "products": 137, "early_access": false}
