{"product_id": "48190", "page": 194, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-24", "text": "A solid offering in the AC franchise. The story here is the main driver, as there isn't a lot to differentiate from AC2 otherwise.", "hours": 19.3, "username": "maalorn", "products": 895, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "48190", "page": 194, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-24", "text": "So first off, Uplay. Ew. And figuring it out can be a pain. But Brotherhood is an excellent game. Traversing Rome (which is absolutely gorgeous) by way of the roofs, streets, or on horseback is enjoyable. The combat system is fluid and easy to master while still being fun. You start the game feeling like a badass and end feeling like an even badasser badass. Slowly taking over the city and recruiting and upgrading your assassins is gratifying. The missions aren't incredibly varied (though some differ incredibly, like the ones with Leonardo da Vinci's war machines) but they remain fun, because, again, you feel like a badass. I'd definitely recommend this game, even at full price.", "hours": 25.0, "username": "Good Drink", "products": 183, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "48190", "page": 195, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-24", "text": "Truly one of my favourite Assassins Creed Games, continueing the story of Ezio Auditore. Many new features and weapons have been added so that you do not feel the game getting repetitive in any way. Its truely a in depth and wonderufl experience growing with Ezio as he gets older and ventures forward to beat the Templars and continue his quest to find more information of the pieces of eden and those who came before. I highly recomened to those who already played Assassins Creed 2 and to anyone esle who wants to enjoy a game with great graphics and an in depth adventure!", "hours": 2.4, "user_id": "76561198033981064", "username": "spartan-2694", "products": 27, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "48190", "page": 195, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-24", "text": "This is a really good game!!!! Sadly, very few people play multiplayer. but there is something so satisfying about seeing an oversized syringe get slammed into your targets neck", "hours": 58.7, "username": "U Just Activated My Alu-card", "products": 146, "early_access": false}
