{"product_id": "48190", "page": 195, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-23", "text": "I bought this game right after I came back from Rome and I loved every minute of it. The star of these games is the setting and  I felt like I was back in Rome again while playing this.", "hours": 58.4, "username": "ainmosni", "products": 277, "early_access": false}
