{"product_id": "48190", "page": 195, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-22", "text": "While a bit short, in my opinion it was more interesting and fun than Assassin's Creed 2.\nIf you finished AC2 and are hungry for more content, this will be perfect for you, it somehow managed to make something amazing even better.\n___\nEnquanto um pouco curto, na minha opini\u00e3o ele foi mais interessante e divertido do que o Assassin's Creed 2.\nSe voc\u00ea terminou o AC2 e est\u00e1 faminto por mais conte\u00fado, isso vai ser perfeito pra voc\u00ea, ele de algum jeito conseguiu fazer algo incr\u00edvel ainda melhor.", "hours": 50.4, "username": "Mega", "products": 434, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "48190", "page": 195, "page_order": 7, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-02-22", "text": "It does not work on Mac (at the very least).", "hours": 29.1, "user_id": "76561198069759499", "username": "bjgerard", "products": 142, "early_access": false}
