{"product_id": "48190", "page": 196, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-21", "text": "Assassins Creed is one of my favorite Video Game series of all time. I have all the games on the Xbox but then I got curiousity to try it out on the computer. The graphics are 101% Amazing, and after mastering the controls. I am now an assassin of the PC version. DEFINITELY buy, it it worth it.", "hours": 80.9, "username": "Omega", "products": 139, "early_access": false}
