{"product_id": "48190", "page": 198, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-04", "text": "Finish\nand you'll know whether you want to play Brotherhood, which serves to extend the storyline and gameplay of its predecessor.\nAs a fan of the epic nature of the series, Brotherhood was a satisfying experience, if somewhat tedious in parts (I found myself watching another screen while playing through the more mundane activities, and idled in-game for for several hours while AFK, waiting to earn income for city improvements), however by the end I was excited to continue the adventure in the \"Ezio\" trilogy finale\n.\n- Skinny from the Fat B*stard", "hours": 169.7, "user_id": "76561198006934852", "username": "-- ExotixisT -- (eks-ot'i-sist)", "products": 1766, "early_access": false}
