{"product_id": "48190", "page": 199, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-01-31", "text": "This was my introduction to the Assassin's Creed franchise.  I chose to try this one first because it seemed to be the best reviewed entry.  I thoroughly enjoyed it.  You have so much freedom to do missions as you like, and the parkour and platforming is very well done.  It deserves all the praise it has received.  It's not without its flaws, but it's such a fun game.\nI regret not purchasing the whole series while they were on sale during Christmas.  I hope there's another Steam sale for this franchise soon.", "hours": 11.6, "user_id": "76561198075984386", "username": "thehappypumpkin", "products": 87, "early_access": false}
