{"product_id": "48190", "page": 201, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-01-13", "text": "Score : 9/10\n+ Like other game of AC series, great fighting and free running system.\n+ A lot of various side quest and activity.\n+ u can recruit ur own assassin brotherhood for help u to assassinate or fight enemy.\n+ all collectible marked on map but u have to buy some treasure map.\n- investment in shop is online. It sounds good but it often disable and take a time for load in investment page. It's unnecessarily to be online. I understand that developer try to annoy piracy but the victem is license customer.\n- Sometimes, the fighting and movement lock on system is very troublesome.", "hours": 73.8, "username": "Iwantto Playagame", "products": 785, "early_access": false}
