{"product_id": "48190", "page": 204, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-01-02", "text": "This is a fun game, but the community is horrid and the single-player in my opinion was boring. Multi-player is a lot of fun but people seem to be.. cheating somehow? Or at a higher rank you have ridiculous spy capabilities.. that in itself, ruin the multiplayer? It's.. odd. Anyways. It's fun, but meh. Community kind of ruins it. It's also at least since last I was on, kind of dead. great FUN with FRIENDS. I don't recommend playing online with random people though. With friends yes, online, no. Maybe you'll get lucky though, who knows. I enjoy it though. Multiplayer anyways. :D", "hours": 9.4, "user_id": "76561198045648963", "username": "Vicccious", "products": 1242, "early_access": false}
