{"product_id": "48190", "page": 214, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-09-29", "text": "I have a serious problem with Assassin's Creed, in the moment when i started to play i lose the time in my mind. This game is incredible, almost perfect for me.\n\u272c The game is from 2007. So the graphics are not the best, but the game is only good with graphics, are same of\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\n\u272c The storyline are amazing. You will be amazed with the game for this.\n\n\u272cThe gameplay is excellent, better than Assassin's Creed II\n\u272c A lot of optional missions, so you will never be stopped\n\u272c The game helps you, but don't let you have a lot of challenges\n\u272c Something i dont like is the gameplay in the boat, is the worse, like the Assassin's Creed II, sorry, its my opinion. The game have some bugs\n\u272c Scenario in Roma is awesome\n\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2606  4/5", "hours": 61.6, "username": "\u019dayuki \u52c7\u6c17", "products": 283, "early_access": false}
