{"product_id": "48190", "page": 215, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-09-07", "text": "Bigger than the first and second games of the series it adds a few new features. The story continues with beautiful graphics and great soundtrack as usual. The combination of real locations, historic characters and fiction is really good!\n--------\nPortuguese translation:\nMaior que os primeiros dois jogos da s\u00e9rie esse jogo adiciona algumas novidades. A hist\u00f3ria de Ezio Auditore continua, com belos gr\u00e1ficos e \u00f3tima trilha sonora. \u00c9 muito legal a combina\u00e7\u00e3o de locais reais com riqueza de detalhes e personagens hist\u00f3ricas e como misturam isso com a fic\u00e7\u00e3o!", "hours": 46.8, "username": "K-Boom", "products": 4189, "early_access": false}
