{"product_id": "48190", "page": 218, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-07-12", "text": "A great improvement over Assassins Creed II. Great storyline and setting. A ridiculous amount of things to do. There is some weirdness in the end with the plot but maybe they just rushed it. I highly recommend this 8/10.", "hours": 276.6, "username": "sonderkraftfahrzeug", "products": 538, "early_access": false}
