{"product_id": "48190", "page": 218, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-07-01", "text": "Until Assassin's Creed IV came out, Brotherhood was my favourite game of the series. The best story (both for Desmond, and for Ezio) and improvements on some of the weaker systems from AC2.", "hours": 40.3, "username": "Matt", "products": 401, "early_access": false}
