{"product_id": "48190", "page": 219, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-06-30", "text": "Best AC game I've played! The story and setting is awesome, great graphics (especially for it's time!) and runs well even on low end specs.There's absolutely nothing I dislike about it as of writing this recommendation and I'm fairly close to the end. 10/10.", "hours": 13.7, "username": "UTINI!!", "products": 302, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "48190", "page": 219, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-06-27", "text": "AC: Brotherhood is another amazing game in the AC series. They tweaked the controls even more, enhanced the graphics, and even made the combat a fluid and exciting system. Ubisoft continues to excel and improving this series. If you love AC, you owe it to yourself to give this one a shot!", "hours": 35.1, "username": "defiance5050", "products": 607, "early_access": false}
