{"product_id": "48190", "page": 220, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-05-21", "text": "Well, actually my favourite Assassin creed game is the second title but i have it in another website. Brotherhood tries to follow the same way of the second, with secondary missions less tedious (as tedious as the first title). I think the goal is having the player in game the more possible hours. The story is nice like the others and you can do a lot of things, fight, jump, climb, etc.\nI saw in this game missions like Tomb Rider saga. To me its impossible not to recomend at least 1 game of Assassin's creed series.", "hours": 29.7, "user_id": "76561198039143385", "username": "Monkey see, monkey do", "products": 129, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "48190", "page": 220, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-05-14", "text": "The best game in the series by far. It keeps things simple in (mostly) a single city and builds on the core gameplay established in ACII. If you are going to play one AC game play this one its truly amazing!", "hours": 15.4, "user_id": "76561197970329460", "username": "Aeneas2020", "products": 542, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "48190", "page": 220, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-05-10", "text": "one of the best assassins creeds that have been out so far and i cant stress how good brotherhood is its just so good 10/10 for me and it just added so much more to the game and took it to a new level.", "hours": 9.2, "user_id": "76561198010540441", "username": "Metalsage", "products": 342, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "48190", "page": 220, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-04-30", "text": "I came out of this game 2 or 3 times and even get tired :-) as the game type and the story is UNSURPASSED quality of the game is super easy and a great multiplayer\nTRY IT ;-)", "hours": 43.1, "username": "Gaben", "products": 357, "early_access": false}
