{"product_id": "48190", "page": 221, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-03-29", "text": "A purely awesome game. Even after you complete the story, there are many other side objectives to complete, and I mean, come on, free-running across buildings and strategically planning assassinations never get's old, when in Rome ;) Although it is worth adding that I would not suggest purchasing the game for it's multi-player,  since there are problems searching for sessions, AND it's scarce to see someone actually searching for one. However, the great single-player definately makes up for that. All-in-all, this game is great and I would seriously recommend it. :D", "hours": 35.1, "username": "dipnug", "products": 47, "early_access": false}
