{"product_id": "48190", "page": 240, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2012-03-27", "text": "Multiplayer is a blast! Highly recommend.", "hours": 27.8, "username": "cr0w9", "products": 533, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "48190", "page": 240, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2012-03-26", "text": "A combination of parkour, swordsmanship and stealth happening in a wonderfully reconstructed Renenaissance Italy - one of the few games that I can play for many hours on end without getting bored.\nMultiplayer is both fast paced *and* rewards cunning, a very interesting diversion from the story mode whose only drawback is that there are often too few players online outside peak hours.\nEndorsed!", "hours": 18.3, "username": "Mr. Pootin", "products": 246, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "48190", "page": 240, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2012-03-19", "text": "Improves from the 2nd game in many areas: Combat, Store and Weapon Upgrading, Interesting Missions.\nIf you just do the required missions, YOU WILL HAVE NO FUN IN THIS GAME... just saying\nPlay it correctly and its worth the money", "hours": 58.1, "username": "IAmTheTrueDuck [Matt]", "products": 263, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "48190", "page": 240, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2012-03-10", "text": "Assassin's Creed Part 3: Assassin's Creed 2 part 2", "hours": 37.1, "username": "Dire Miralis", "products": 318, "early_access": false}
